==About==
===Format===
* '''IN-Game Qualifiers:''''' July 27th - August 2nd, 2026
* '''Round 1:''''' August 10th - 15th
** 256 teams qualify for Round 2.

* '''Round 2:''''' August 20th - 23th, 2026
** 256 teams
** 64 teams qualify for Quarter Finals

* '''Quarter Finals:''''' August 27th - 30th, 2026
** 64 teams
** 32 teams qualify for Semi Finals

* '''Semi Finals''''' Sept 3rd - 6th
** 32 teams
** 16 teams qualify for Road to Masters Finals

* '''Road to Masters Finals:''''' Sept 8th - 10th, 2026
** 16 Teams, 3 matchdays.
** 18 matches (6 each day).
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 8 teams}} qualify for '''[[Trident Ignite/2026/Challengers vs Masters|Challengers vs Masters]]'''

